                  <h3>Super-Fast Mercury Satellite Internet Connects You Efficiently </h3>
                  <p>Rural high speed satellite Internet service ensures that you  have the kind of speed you want in order to do the things you dream of doing  online: downloads, social media, streaming media and more. </p>
                  
                  <img src="images/feat-speed.gif" alt="Satellite Internet plans provides Downloads up to 15/mbps" title="Downloads up to 15/mbps" class="right"/><p> Mercury Satellite  delivers speeds that are unparalleled by the competitors: as fast as 15 Mbps  for downloads and 2 Mbps for uploads. It uses the exclusive Mercury Satellite technology, the best in the industry. The developers of this technology are  constantly striving to improve upon the already outstanding service, ensuring  that Mercury Satellite always delivers cutting edge speed.</p>
                  <h3>Mercury Satellite Has What You Need</h3>
                  <p>With the goal of always offering exactly what rural  customers are looking for in satellite Internet service, Mercury Satellite  offers 4 different plans so you can choose the perfect one to meet your needs. Whether  you occasionally use the Internet or have a household full of regular online  users, there is a Mercury Satellite plan with the speed and data access you  require. In addition, no matter what kind of computer operating system you  have, Mercury Satellite Internet works for you. Enjoy the always-on connection  that is secure and responsive, exactly what you are looking for. <br>
                    When it comes to satellite Internet service providers in rural  America, few compare to Mercury Satellite, the provider that prioritizes bring  high quality, high speed rural broadband service to absolutely every part of  the country. Make the change today and upgrade to Mercury Satellite Internet  Service. </p>
